attributes.name: content-security-policy
attributes.content: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-eval' https://api.pin.net.au https://api.stripe.com 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; font-src data:; img-src *; media-src 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-src *;  report-uri /log/csp
